</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_265" id="132v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_265_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Engelhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von Eberſtein <expan>thumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l2"><expan>vvırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> . vnd <expan>lantrıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> des <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒogentums</expan> ʒu <expan>frank<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_265_r1l3">Erſamer lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt . von <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vvalkan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l4">von Meinbernheım . Vnd des vıſchel Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns geſeſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l6">etc . Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wır </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_265_r1l5">wır </ab></add> wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l7">wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> vıſchel Juden für vns beſant vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒurede geſacʒt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l8"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wıe er vor etwıeuıl <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> auf den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l9"><expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> walkan / vor dem <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> des Burggraftums ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l10"><expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> erklagt vnd ʒu echt bracht hab . vvıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> . ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l11">doch den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Juden vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>erbett<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ er dıe ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l12">vnd ſeine erklagte recht gen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> walkan . in gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l13">wıl anſteen <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . / 
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo </del> <expan>hieʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ſand Johanns tag ſün = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l14">wenden ſchıerıſt . Mıt der <expan>beſcheıdenh<ex>eit</ex></expan> . Jſt daʒ Jm oder <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l15"><expan>ſcheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> von dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> walkan . freẅntlıchs ſleẅnıgs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l16"><expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ʒeıt <expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan> wırt vnd dem <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> gnug beſchıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l17">daʒ denn . ſeine erklagten recht vnd echt abſein . vnd auch alſo daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l18">er <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein ſcheinbott frıd vnd geleyt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das recht von Jm ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l19"><expan>ſuche<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>eincʒubrıng<ex>en</ex></expan> / geſchech <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> des niht . ſo maint ſıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l20">der <expan>obg<ex>ena</ex>nt</expan> Jud nach ſand Johanns tag ſeiner erklagten recht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l21">wıder ʒu halten . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_265_r1l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> mathıe <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_265" id="132v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Engelhart<ex>en</ex></expan> von Eberstein,
                            <expan>thumh<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
                        und <expan>lantricht<ex>er</ex></expan> des
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogentums</expan> zu <expan>Frank<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer, lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als ir uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        habt von <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Walkan von Meinbernheim und des
                        Vischel, juden, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns gesessen etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>wir</add> wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz wir <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        Vischel, juden, für uns besant und <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu rede
                        gesaczt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Der hat uns
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, wie er vor etwievil
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> auf den
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Walkan vor dem
                            <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> des burggraftums zu
                                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> erklagt und zu echt bracht hab.
                        Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir doch
                        den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> juden umb
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>erbett<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz er die sache und seine erklagte recht
                        gen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Walkan in gut wil ansteen
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> und <app>
<note><q type="date">sand Johanns tag sünwenden
                                schierist</q>24.06.1416</note>
</app> mit der <expan>bescheidenh<ex>eit</ex></expan> ist, daz im oder
                                <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> von dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Walkan frewntlichs slewnigs
                                <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        zeit <expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan> wirt und dem
                            <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> gnug beschiht, daz denn seine erklagten
                        recht und echt absein und auch also, daz er <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        sein scheinbott frid und geleyt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das recht von
                        im zu <expan>suche<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>einczubring<ex>en</ex></expan>. Geschech
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> des niht, so maint sich der
                                <expan>obg<ex>ena</ex>nt</expan> jud nach sand Johanns tag seiner
                        erklagten recht wider zu halten. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Mathie <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li.</expan>
</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
